Package org.ow2.bonita.facade.def.majorElement

Contains interfaces relating to definitions elements.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ActivityDefinition This interface represents the activity definition.
DataFieldDefinition This interface represents the DataField definition.
DescriptionElement DescriptionElement within a BPM Element
EventProcessDefinition  
NamedElement NamedElement within a BPM Element
ParticipantDefinition This interface represents the Participant definition.
It's derived from the Workflow Participant of XPDL.
The Participant entity type attribute characterises the participant to be an individual, an organisational unit or an abstract resource such as a machine.
ProcessDefinition This interface represents the Process definition.
ProcessElement Parent interface for interfaces into majorElement package.
TransitionDefinition Activities are linked themselves using transition.
 

Enum Summary

ProcessDefinition.ProcessState Process state are used to define the process life cycle.
A process can be enable, disable several times.
